== 贝斯特曼改进法 ==
{{main|贝斯特曼-大平试剂}}
通过[[1-重氮基-2-氧代丙基膦酸二甲酯|1-重氮基-2-氧代丙基膦酸二甲酯]]（贝斯特曼试剂）与甲醇和碳酸钾反应，在反应体系中原位产生赛费特-吉尔伯特试剂。

* 贝斯特曼试剂与醛生成末炔的反应一般产率很高。<ref name="muller1996">{{cite journal en| author = S. Müller, B. Liepold, G. Roth and H. J. Bestmann* | title = An Improved One-pot Procedure for the Synthesis of Alkynes from Aldehydes | year = 1996 | journal = [[Synlett|Synlett]] | volume = 1996| issue = 06 | pages = 521–522 | doi = 10.1055/s-1996-5474}}</ref><ref name="roth2004">{{cite journal en| author = G. Roth, B. Liepold, S. Müller and H. J. Bestmann | title = Further Improvements of the Synthesis of Alkynes from Aldehydes | year = 2004 | journal = [[Synthesis_(journal)|Synthesis]] | volume = 2004| issue = 1 | pages = 59–62 | doi = 10.1055/s-2003-44346}}</ref>
* 碳酸钾是较温和的试剂，其使用增加了底物官能团的耐受性。

